data.description: Prepare to be impressed by this remarkable 4-bedroom, 3-bath home nestled on a sprawling 1.21-acre lot in Pickett Downs.  The modern kitchen dazzles with stainless steel appliances, a gas stove, and a walk-in pantry.  The open floor plan features bamboo and tile floors and a cozy gas fireplace.  The spacious primary bedroom boasts a walk-in closet.  No carpet ensures easy maintenance throughout the home.  Property updates – roof (2022), pool pump (2023), upgraded kitchen (2019), water heater (2018) and a/c (2015).    Step outside to a pool with fountains or relax on the expansive front porch.  A handy storage shed or workspace adds practicality and the 2-car garage has been converted into a game room/additional living space for endless fun.  Top-rated schools in the area make this property a dream for families seeking both space and education.  Plus, a fenced yard offers privacy and security.
